CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "Having Fun at Frog's Dance were these localities, left to right: Mr. and Mrs. James Goode, Mrs. Leon Waddy, Vivian Scott Hale, Evelyn and Morgan Thomas, the Walter Hales, Dr. Leon Waddy and the William Crawfords. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group, from left: Louisa Jeffries Webster Goode, James Goode, Mable Waddy, Vivian Scott Hale, Evelyn Thomas, Morgan Thomas, Mr. and Mrs. Walter Hale, Dr. Leon Waddy, Pauline Lowry Crawford, and William Henry Crawford, gathered around banquet table for FROGS event, Gateway Plaza, another version
